---
// src/components/Stories.astro
---
<section class="py-24 px-6 overflow-hidden" id="stories">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold tracking-wider text-sm uppercase">Community</span>
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mt-4 tracking-tight">Loved by 1,000+ Makers</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 relative">
            
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-orange-100 dark:border-neutral-800 transform md:-rotate-1 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-300">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-1 text-primary mb-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-rounded">star</span><span class="material-symbols-rounded">star</span><span class="material-symbols-rounded">star</span><span class="material-symbols-rounded">star</span><span class="material-symbols-rounded">star</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl italic font-serif leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    "I used to track my pottery orders in a notebook. Panchasara professionalized my entire studio. My customers love how easy it is to shop."
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-orange-200 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
                        <img alt="Sarah J." class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1438761681033-6461ffad8d80?q=80&w=200&auto=format&fit=crop"/>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold">Sarah J.</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Mud & Clay Studio</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-orange-100 dark:border-neutral-800 transform md:rotate-1 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-300 md:mt-12">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-1 text-primary mb-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-rounded">star</span><span class="material-symbols-rounded">star</span><span class="material-symbols-rounded">star</span><span class="material-symbols-rounded">star</span><span class="material-symbols-rounded">star</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl italic font-serif leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    "Managing custom jewelry requests via DM was a nightmare. Now I have a proper catalog with variations for size and metal. It's a game changer."
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-orange-200 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
                        <img alt="Marcus K." class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500648767791-00dcc994a43e?q=80&w=200&auto=format&fit=crop"/>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold">Marcus K.</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Luxe Artisan Gems</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-orange-100 dark:border-neutral-800 transform md:-rotate-1 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-300">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-1 text-primary mb-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-rounded">star</span><span class="material-symbols-rounded">star</span><span class="material-symbols-rounded">star</span><span class="material-symbols-rounded">star</span><span class="material-symbols-rounded">star</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl italic font-serif leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    "The pre-order system is a lifesaver for my sourdough drops. I sell out in minutes and don't have to chase a single payment."
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-orange-200 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
                        <img alt="Elena R." class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?q=80&w=200&auto=format&fit=crop"/>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold">Elena R.</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Elena's Sourdough</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>